	<!-- Vaultsword -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_TotE_BaseMakeableMelee">
		<defName>GW_TotE_Vaultsword</defName>
		<label>Vaultsword</label>
		<description>A special type of ancient powersword wielded only by Blade Champions of the Adeptus Custodes. Wielded in the Hurricanis style, the Vaultsword can output an incredible storm of deadly, armor-penetrating strikes.\n\nVaultswords are a piece of “archeotech”, not to be confused with archotech of the rimworlds. “Archeotech” is an Imperial term linked to “archeology”; it means once-lost technology that was recovered from ancient times, such as the Dark Age of Technology.</description>
